# Allowlist — ignore everything at the repo root by default...
/*

# ...except the SOURCE files. The site (index.html + images/) is BUILT by the
# GitHub Action and published straight to Pages — it is never committed, so it
# can never cause a merge conflict.
!/build
!/.github
!/DEPLOY.md
!/SETUP-GITHUB.md
!/.gitignore

# Generated / local artifacts — never commit:
build/node_modules/
**/.DS_Store
/_site/
